  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Patients under 18 years of age&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  With a diagnosis of CD&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Who have completed remission induction with biologic therapy&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Who are on maintenance biologic therapy&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Present calprotectin values higher than the limit values established by the laboratory&#xD;
             (higher than 250 ug/g).&#xD;
&#xD;
        Exclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Children who are unable to receive enteral dietary intake&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Comorbidities affecting nutritional status and/or bone metabolism, growth or pubertal&#xD;
             development&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Children already on special diets&#xD;
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
